wiki.summary: Britney recorded three songs with T-Pain, only one (that he wrote and did not produce) was released ("Hot As Ice") and was produced by Danja. The two unreleased songs he collaborated on with her and produced are titled "Boyfriend" and "One Of A Kind."    "They are rebellious songs," says T-Pain, 20, born Faheem Najim. "It's her letting everybody know she doesn't care about all the crap going on in the media."
